Package: libcamiface-basler
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, basler-pylon
Suggests: coriander
Provides: libcamiface
Conflicts: libcamiface, libcamiface-prosilica, libcamiface-avt
Replaces: libcamiface, libcamiface-prosilica, libcamiface-avt
Description: cross-platform cross-backend camera driver (library)
 cam_iface is the core package of several in the motmot
 repository that are involved with digital camera acquisition
 and analysis

